<sub><italic>jkt</italic></sub> is the effect of the <italic>k</italic>th genotype of the <italic>j</italic>th marker at the <italic>t</italic>th time point, with the restriction<disp-formula id="Equ2"><label>2</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M3">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
