      <p id="Par29">The first and second derivatives involved in Eqs. (15) and (16) can be derived as in Additional file <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media">1</xref>: Appendixes S1 and S2. We chose a proper index for discriminating QTL patterns by assessing the power of each criterion through computer simulations.</p>
